    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong finish, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with only slight creasing on the driver's seat bolster and minimal wear on the primary touchpoints. It runs smoothly, handles well, and represents a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for pre-owned vehicle.",
